entire bill and insert
13
14 “An Act relating to nuisances; amending 50 O.S. 2021,

Section 3:
Sections 2, 8, 10, and 21, which relate to public
15 nuisances, remedies, and civil action; prohibiting
certain acts from being deemed public nuisance;
16 clarifying applicable remedies in certain civil
actions; requiring certain determination for
17 liability in certain action; requiring determination
of proximate cause for maintenance of certain action;
18 specifying certain unlawful acts as public nuisance;
and providing an effective date.
